OL,4,ETeletext50 Art Exhibition    S #///'!  
OL,6,BTo celebrate five decades of teletext, 
OL,7,BCeefax'sEgolden anniversary,Bwe are    
OL,8,Bhosting an online festival of teletext 
OL,9,Bart.                                   
OL,11,BArtists were asked to respond to the   
OL,12,Bfollowing prompts:                     
OL,14,EBWhat else was happening inE1974?     
OL,15,EBHow would you celebrate teletext's   
OL,16,  E50th birthday?                       
OL,17,EBWhat other significantEeventsBtook   
OL,18,  Bplace during teletext's lifetime?    
