OL,4,EYour art shown in Finland!   S #///'!  
OL,6,BOurE50th anniversaryBartworks will be  
OL,7,Bshown on Finnish public teletext in    
OL,8,BOctober 2024, and we are offering you  
OL,9,Bthe opportunity to beEexhibited!       
OL,11,BSimply add your art toEChunkytextBand  
OL,12,Bit will be put forward for broadcast.  
OL,13,BIf you wish to be attributed, don't    
OL,14,Bforget to add your name/alias to your  
OL,15,Bartwork.                               
OL,17,BThe final deadline for submissions will
OL,18,Bbe the end ofESeptember 2024.          
