OL,4,EYour art shown in Finland!   S #///'!  
OL,6,BBy submitting pages to be shown onEYle,
OL,7,Byou retain full copyright of your art  
OL,8,Bbut give yourEpermissionBfor it to be  
OL,9,Bshown on Yle and an archive to be kept 
OL,10,BatEDemozoo.org.                        
OL,12,BYou can enter as many pages as you     
OL,13,Blike, but be aware thatEcopyrighted    
OL,14,EcharactersBmay not be suitable for Yle.
OL,16,BYou don't have to respond to the       
